<paragraph id="4B5B2900DB6CC47A09E3FE73CE5EFDF7" blockId="4.[166,1225,262,577]" pageId="4" pageNumber="99">
Note. Heroiske Vill. (
<collectingRegion id="8920E7E2DB6CC47A08C3FE73CD65FE57" box="[507,610,455,481]" country="Ukraine" name="Kherson" pageId="4" pageNumber="99">Kherson</collectingRegion>
Reg.) is the westernmost known locality. Being abundant on saline marshes, the species has a highly patched distribution: viz., in the Pryazovslyi NNP, it was found in two localities out of five, although all of them host vast saline marshes.
</paragraph>
